lead_paragraph: Fresh off his impressive showing at the Masters, PGA Tour rookie and former LSU golfer Smylie Kaufman is preparing for another heaping of fanfare at the Zurich Classic.

headline.print_headline: Kaufman Aims to Feed Off Fan Support at Zurich Classic
